{"quotes": [{"lines": [{"text": "Why were those people shot?", "character": "Maj. Robert Dapes", "characterId": "nm0000125"}, {"text": "Perhaps they tried to escape.", "character": "Capt. Raphael Ramirez", "characterId": "nm0001185"}, {"text": "From what?", "character": "Maj. Robert Dapes", "characterId": "nm0000125"}, {"text": "From being shot.", "character": "Capt. Raphael Ramirez", "characterId": "nm0001185"}, {"text": "But how did they know they were rebels?", "character": "Maj. Robert Dapes", "characterId": "nm0000125"}, {"text": "Because they tried to escape.", "character": "Capt. Raphael Ramirez", "characterId": "nm0001185"}, {"text": "Well, wouldn't you?", "character": "Maj. Robert Dapes", "characterId": "nm0000125"}, {"text": "Of course.", "character": "Capt. Raphael Ramirez", "characterId": "nm0001185"}, {"text": "Are you a rebel?", "character": "Maj. Robert Dapes", "characterId": "nm0000125"}, {"text": "If I try to escape, I am. Wasn't it the same in Malaya? You didn't know them till they ran.", "character": "Capt. Raphael Ramirez", "characterId": "nm0001185"}, {"text": "No, it wasn't!", "character": "Maj. Robert Dapes", "characterId": "nm0000125"}, {"text": "Very well, you're here to teach us!", "character": "Capt. Raphael Ramirez", "characterId": "nm0001185"}, {"text": "[Ramirez is shot dead.]", "character": null, "characterId": null}]}, {"lines": [{"text": "It's not like you to be so unselfish.", "character": "Juan Pulido", "characterId": "nm0001697"}, {"text": "It's not like you to notice.", "character": "Alexandra Lopez de Pulido", "characterId": "nm0000724"}]}, {"lines": [{"text": "[confronting a woman guerilla]\nIt's a girl! I want to question her.", "character": "Maj. Robert Dapes", "characterId": "nm0000125"}, {"text": "Yes. First you, then she is 'questioned' by the sergeant and each of the men as many times as possible, and then two or three days later she is taken and shot. It would be much kinder to shoot her now.", "character": "Capt. Raphael Ramirez", "characterId": "nm0001185"}]}, {"lines": [{"text": "[to bellboy in cheap hotel]\nI want a room with water which is sometimes hot. If there's a bath to put it in, I wouldn't mind.", "character": "Maj. Robert Dapes", "characterId": "nm0000125"}]}, {"lines": [{"text": "Major, tell me what your favorite weapon is, and I'll get it for you, whatever it is.", "character": "Gen. Bello", "characterId": "nm0000842"}, {"text": "Brains!", "character": "Maj. Robert Dapes", "characterId": "nm0000125"}]}, {"lines": [{"text": "Even a blind eye can be poked out.", "character": "Maj. Robert Dapes", "characterId": "nm0000125"}]}]}